We don't usually check gates like this in validation - we check them in `dropDisabled`, and then here we do:

```
if gate enabled && value == nil {
    error - required
} else if value != nil && invalid value {
    error - notSupported
}
```

Then, wehn the gate goes away it becomes:

```
if value == nil {
    error - required
} else if invalid value {
    error - notSupported
}
```

