Consider 2 candidates:
1: { binVersion=1.32, compatVersion=1.30 }
2: { binVersion=1.31, compatVersion=1.31 }

Who should win the lease?

Can you spec this out a bit more?  e.g.

"""
    // OldestCompatibilityVersion picks the oldest LeaseCandidate, where
    // "oldest" is defined as follows.  1) Select the candidate(s) with the lowest binary version.
    // 2) If multiple candidates have the same binary version, select the candidate(s) with the 
	// lowest compatibility version.  3) If multiple candidates have the same compatibility version, select the 
    //  candidate with the most recent creationTimestamp.  If a candidate specifies a binary version but not a 
