We have argued a bit about whether the origin for this should be the underlying format (in which case why bother using `ValidateNodeName()`? Just call `IsDNSSubdomain()`) or the abstraction of "node name" (in which case which core concepts are exposed?

If you consider API machinery as "bigger than just kubernetes", then "Node" is a layering inversion.  The API machinery doesn't know about nodes.

@jpbetz

